Guardar los datos en el hdfs
  hdfs dfs -put libros

Ejecutar el hadoop con mas de un reducer
  sudo /usr/bin/hadoop jar /usr/lib/hadoop-mapreduce/hadoop-streaming-2.6.0-cdh5.7.0.jar -D mapreduce.job.reduces=2 -input libros -output salida_libros -mapper mapper.py -reducer reducer.py -file mapper.py -file reducer.py

Ejecutar solo el mapper
  sudo /usr/bin/hadoop jar /usr/lib/hadoop-mapreduce/hadoop-streaming-2.6.0-cdh5.7.0.jar -input libros -output salida_temperaturas -mapper mapper.py -file mapper.py